      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NOAKI WARRIOR (4) finds it hard to win. Finished in the money last time though when third (16.76) at this track. Makes plenty of appeal. SHE'S BUBBLES (2) drew an outside box and was game in defeat when only 1.75 lengths from the winner Whispering Mist in third(16.72) at this track. Likely to be in the finish again. GYPSY GIRL PEARL (1) was out of character last run when missing the frame, finishing fifth (35.22) in a Grade 4/5 at Q Parklands. Normally safely away but always well back and facing a task from wide out last time. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Warrants plenty of respect. LITTLE ROWDY (6) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
